---
title: Veggie Beyond Meat® Chili with Tortilla Chips
description: Simple but fantastic, this delicious chili is filled with Beyond Meat®, beans, bell peppers and tomatoes. Each bite is tender and comforting. We suggest using the tortilla chips to scoop up and enjoy every last drop!
